{"tid":105263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抄明將！！ 銀座專門店推出限定Kitkat壽司  ！！","createTime":"2017-02-02T17:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T05:38:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef18c68b31a21a264b7d663f32c1ee67384a4022","tid":105263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"31.01.2017<br />\n <br />\nKitkat專門店「KITKAT Chocolatory」銀座店將於2月2日13時30分開張，為了記念新店鋪而推出的Kitkat壽司亦會同時開始發售。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 米通配上獨特的新口味Kitkat<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi01.jpg&h=37912235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28b9296201b40f85e25e337aba28634d805315e6","tid":105263,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f411e1f87c8c1e2f734ed1fb848314f8e0bb0","tid":105263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"▼ 吞拿魚（紅苺味）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi03.jpg&h=75b42548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 海膽（北海道蜜瓜味）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi04.jpg&h=7f712c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 玉子（南瓜布甸味）<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi02.jpg&h=b91e25d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ae54d507e6aaa5d06ce0be9e3a66a92a57c7ab8","tid":105263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"▼ 這次的Kitkat壽司一套三件，還會附送竹葉，提高像真度。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi05.jpg&h=b3db2ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nKitkat準備了500份Kitkat壽司贈送給（買滿3000千日元的）顧客，由2月2日至14日，每日只限送10份，數量有限送完即止。<br />\n<br />\n▼情人節限定的「スペシャルアソート銀座デザイン（Special Assort Ginza Design）」（1350円）"},{"pid":"6b6d6c27eac09bf86729225aeaf3f397fc2a3f80","tid":105263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi08.jpg&h=28de391e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼ 外表是很可愛啦&hellip;&hellip;但大概會吃到一地都是碎屑&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi06.jpg&h=3d542b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKITKAT FACTORY 銀座店<br />\n營業時間：10時～20時<br />\n地址：東京都中央區銀座3-7-2<br />\n聯絡電話：03-6228-6285<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1701/31/l_kh_170130sushi09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.itmedia.co.jp%2Fnl%2Farticles%2F1701%2F31%2Fl_kh_170130sushi09.jpg&h=e4743980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=4573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D4573&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=77f458d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=4573</a>"},{"pid":"b94f9af2be